description: When Americans think about fighting China, the first things that come to mind are recruitment, weapons development, and our military industrial base. It’s important that we prioritize all three. Until recently, our Armed Forces were experiencing historic recruitment shortfalls. Our procurement system is badly broken, regularly delivering weapons platforms years late and billions over budget. […]
